S.FORM: Giannis Antetokounmpo nalecuhan i Athens, Greece, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw(pahanhanan tu kawaw ) ayza. Giannis Antetokounmpo i 2013 a mihcaan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka cacay ku uwac atu silsil 15, namapili' tu nu Milwaukee Bucks putiput. 12 a bulad 6 a demiad, 1994 a mihcaan, Giannis Antetokounmpo, miunduay. NBA kanatal kanas mali putiput, Amilika: National Basketball Association, sapuyu'en NBA, u Amis Amilika tatama syubay kanas mali putiput. izaw 30 a mali cebang, mikitinay tusa a subal, sawaliyan atu satipan. cacay subal izaw tulu a cu, cacay a cu izaw lima a cebang, cacay cebang namakay Canada, u zama sa namakay Amilika. kya madademec "Amilika syubay kanas mali nisakaput sasasedsed, acasa "Amilika kanas nisakaput sasasedsed", sapuyu'en "Amilika syubay kanas", acasa kakelul han NBA. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
